                                <p>
                                    Savor the Mediterranean flavors of Grilled Lamb Kebabs with Tzatziki Sauce. 
                                    Juicy, perfectly seasoned lamb skewers grilled to perfection, served with 
                                    a refreshing, creamy tzatziki sauce, make for a dish that's both light and flavorful. 
                                    Perfect for outdoor barbecues and summer dinners
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-lg-4 text-center order-1 order-lg-2">
                                <img src="~/img/restaurant/Lamb-Kebab.jpg" alt="" class="img-fluid">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tab-pane" id="tab-2">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-lg-8 details order-2 order-lg-1">
                                <h3>Roast Beef with Yorkshire Pudding and Gravy</h3>                     
                                <p>
                                    Pudding, and Gravy. Succulent roast beef served with golden, puffed 
                                    Yorkshire puddings and a luscious, savory gravy makes for a meal that's 
                                    both hearty and heartwarming. Ideal for family gatherings and special occasions
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-lg-4 text-center order-1 order-lg-2">
                                <img src="~/img/restaurant/roast-beef.jpeg" alt="" class="img-fluid">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tab-pane" id="tab-3">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-lg-8 details order-2 order-lg-1">
                                <h3>Classic Spaghetti Carbonara</h3>
                                <p>
                                    Indulge in the creamy, savory delight of Classic Spaghetti Carbonara. 
                                    This Italian favorite combines al dente pasta with crispy pancetta, rich egg 
                                    yolks, and a generous sprinkling of Parmesan cheese, all brought together with 
                                    a touch of black pepper. A simple yet decadent dish that's perfect for any occasion
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-lg-4 text-center order-1 order-lg-2">
                                <img src="~/img/restaurant/spaghetti-carbonara.jpg" alt="" class="img-fluid">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tab-pane" id="tab-4">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-lg-8 details order-2 order-lg-1">
                                <h3>Chicken Enchiladas with Red Sauce</h3>
                                <p>
                                    Chicken Enchiladas with Red Sauce bring a burst of vibrant Mexican flavors to your table. 
                                    Tender chicken wrapped in soft tortillas, smothered in a zesty, homemade red sauce, and 
                                    topped with melted cheese—this dish is a fiesta for your taste buds. Ideal for a hearty 
                                    and satisfying meal
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-lg-4 text-center order-1 order-lg-2">
                                <img src="~/img/restaurant/chicken-enchiladas.jpg" alt="" class="img-fluid">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tab-pane" id="tab-5">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-lg-8 details order-2 order-lg-1">
                                <h3>Coq au Vin</h3>
                                <p>
                                    Coq au Vin is a classic French dish that epitomizes rustic elegance. Slow-cooked chicken in 
                                    a rich, red wine sauce, infused with the flavors of garlic, mushrooms, and bacon, creates a 
                                    meal that's both comforting and sophisticated. Perfect for a cozy dinner with loved ones
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-lg-4 text-center order-1 order-lg-2">
                                <img src="~/img/restaurant/cog-au-vin.jpg" alt="" class="img-fluid">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
